## 5. Risk & Mitigation

| # | Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | KB latency > 100ms | High | Local SQLite, benchmark early |
| 2 | Async writes hard to verify | Medium | Await option for test mode |
| 3 | Mock servers mismatch | Medium | Integration tests with real KB |
| 4 | Race conditions | Medium | Test with asyncio.gather() |

